Package: fixeddecimal
Title: Provide simple fixed decimal arithmetic
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: 
    person("micabo", "", , "37561518+micabo@users.noreply.github.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provide fixed decimal arithmetic for simple tasks.
             Basic operations (e.g. +, -, *, /) are implemented, which will
             retain the number of fractional decimal digits of their arguments.
             Results will be rounded away from zero (for *, /, mean, prod).
